{"tid":1815401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停捐保良局 轉捐好鄰舍北區教會 一樣有退稅","createTime":"2020-01-07T13:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T02:21:58.000Z","uid":54623,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"35ca884231eb794f6c79d621f01f65868398fe54","tid":1815401,"uid":54623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5R4K5H1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5R4K5H1.jpg&h=53ac346b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sgd73uy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSgd73uy.jpg&h=ddbeba6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好鄰舍北區教會唔洗介紹喇<br />\n即係陳伯守護孩子班朋友<br />\n<br />\n 請按以下連結填寫捐款/奉獻表格︰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1ONJd9Mozjig1hQGjaIBp0PtIKJJ9diSUGZ-QPnaw38k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1ONJd9Mozjig1hQGjaIBp0PtIKJJ9diSUGZ-QPnaw38k&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=c2c8aeb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1ONJd9Mozjig1hQGjaIBp0PtIKJJ9diSUGZ-QPnaw38k</a><br />\n<br />\n*如欲奉獻予教會，可將奉獻存入中銀戶口 012-590-0-008567-0，並將入數紙電郵至本會；亦可以劃線支票寄往「上水新康街12號2F」給本會，抬頭請寫「好鄰舍北區教會有限公司」/「Good Neighbour North District Church Limited」，並連同姓名、電話、地址/電郵附上。奉獻一百元或以上可獲發免稅收據。【政府慈善團體註冊編號︰91/14411】<br />\n<br />\n*如欲以信用卡作一次性捐款，請click以下：<br />\n<br />\n*如欲獲發收據，可在上面google form link填寫個人資料。捐款100元以上就可獲取收據。<br />\n<a href=\"https://goodneighbournd.wordpress.com/category/%e3%80%90%e5%90%8c%e8%a1%8c%e8%80%85%ef%b8%b0%e5%a5%bd%e9%84%b0%e8%88%8d%e8%a1%97%e5%9d%8a%e8%8c%b6%e5%b1%85%e6%9a%a8%e6%95%99%e6%9c%83%e5%a0%b4%e5%9c%b0%e7%b1%8c%e6%ac%be%e7%af%87%e3%80%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoodneighbournd.wordpress.com%2Fcategory%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%2590%258c%25e8%25a1%258c%25e8%2580%2585%25ef%25b8%25b0%25e5%25a5%25bd%25e9%2584%25b0%25e8%2588%258d%25e8%25a1%2597%25e5%259d%258a%25e